{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":621,"text":"Could I protect my father"},{"time":1993,"text":"from the Armed Islamic Group with a paring knife?"},{"time":5168,"text":"That was the question I faced"},{"time":6729,"text":"one Tuesday morning in June of 1993,"},{"time":9497,"text":"when I was a law student."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11339,"text":"I woke up early that morning"},{"time":13277,"text":"in Dad's apartment"},{"time":14397,"text":"on the outskirts of Algiers, Algeria,"},{"time":16695,"text":"to an unrelenting pounding on the front door."},{"time":19969,"text":"It was a season as described by a local paper"},{"time":22729,"text":"when every Tuesday a scholar fell"},{"time":25585,"text":"to the bullets of fundamentalist assassins."},{"time":28768,"text":"My father's university teaching of Darwin"},{"time":31130,"text":"had already provoked a classroom visit"},{"time":33130,"text":"from the head of the so-called\nIslamic Salvation Front,"},{"time":36601,"text":"who denounced Dad as an advocate of biologism"},{"time":39657,"text":"before Dad had ejected the man,"},{"time":42323,"text":"and now whoever was outside"},{"time":43810,"text":"would neither identify himself nor go away."},{"time":46910,"text":"So my father tried to get the police on the phone,"},{"time":49882,"text":"but perhaps terrified by the rising tide"},{"time":51980,"text":"of armed extremism that had already claimed"},{"time":54404,"text":"the lives of so many Algerian officers,"},{"time":56937,"text":"they didn't even answer."},{"time":59063,"text":"And that was when I went to the kitchen,"},{"time":61402,"text":"got out a paring knife,"},{"time":62777,"text":"and took up a position inside the entryway."},{"time":65755,"text":"It was a ridiculous thing to do, really,"},{"time":67302,"text":"but I couldn't think of anything else,"},{"time":69151,"text":"and so there I stood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71740,"text":"When I look back now, I think\nthat that was the moment"},{"time":74247,"text":"that set me on the path was to writing a book"},{"time":76761,"text":"called \"Your Fatwa Does Not Apply Here:"},{"time":79413,"text":"Untold Stories from the Fight\nAgainst Muslim Fundamentalism.\""},{"time":83450,"text":"The title comes from a Pakistani play."},{"time":86416,"text":"I think it was actually that moment"},{"time":89266,"text":"that sent me on the journey"},{"time":91010,"text":"to interview 300 people of Muslim heritage"},{"time":93960,"text":"from nearly 30 countries,"},{"time":95494,"text":"from Afghanistan to Mali,"},{"time":97910,"text":"to find out how they fought fundamentalism"},{"time":100251,"text":"peacefully like my father did,"},{"time":102479,"text":"and how they coped with the attendant risks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106214,"text":"Luckily, back in June of 1993,"},{"time":108431,"text":"our unidentified visitor went away,"},{"time":111263,"text":"but other families were so much less lucky,"},{"time":114308,"text":"and that was the thought\nthat motivated my research."},{"time":118161,"text":"In any case, someone would return"},{"time":119691,"text":"a few months later and leave a note"},{"time":121275,"text":"on Dad's kitchen table,"},{"time":122727,"text":"which simply said, \"Consider yourself dead.\""},{"time":126857,"text":"Subsequently, Algeria's\nfundamentalist armed groups"},{"time":129845,"text":"would murder as many as 200,000 civilians"},{"time":132908,"text":"in what came to be known"},{"time":134260,"text":"as the dark decade of the 1990s,"},{"time":137138,"text":"including every single one"},{"time":139010,"text":"of the women that you see here."},{"time":142257,"text":"In its harsh counterterrorist response,"},{"time":145130,"text":"the state resorted to torture"},{"time":147127,"text":"and to forced disappearances,"},{"time":148838,"text":"and as terrible as all of these events became,"},{"time":152200,"text":"the international community largely ignored them."},{"time":155835,"text":"Finally, my father, an Algerian\npeasant's son turned professor,"},{"time":159558,"text":"was forced to stop teaching at the university"},{"time":161661,"text":"and to flee his apartment,"},{"time":163850,"text":"but what I will never forget"},{"time":165223,"text":"about Mahfoud Bennoune, my dad,"},{"time":167458,"text":"was that like so many other Algerian intellectuals,"},{"time":170167,"text":"he refused to leave the country"},{"time":171941,"text":"and he continued to publish pointed criticisms,"},{"time":174999,"text":"both of the fundamentalists"},{"time":176949,"text":"and sometimes of the government they battled."},{"time":179919,"text":"For example, in a November 1994 series"},{"time":183041,"text":"in the newspaper El Watan"},{"time":185195,"text":"entitled \"How Fundamentalism"},{"time":186704,"text":"Produced a Terrorism without Precedent,\""},{"time":190246,"text":"he denounced what he called"},{"time":191483,"text":"the terrorists' radical break with the true Islam"},{"time":194816,"text":"as it was lived by our ancestors."},{"time":197684,"text":"These were words that could get you killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200515,"text":"My father's country taught me"},{"time":201992,"text":"in that dark decade of the 1990s that"},{"time":204546,"text":"the popular struggle against Muslim fundamentalism"},{"time":207954,"text":"is one of the most important"},{"time":209642,"text":"and overlooked human rights struggles"},{"time":212173,"text":"in the world."},{"time":213928,"text":"This remains true today, nearly 20 years later."},{"time":217539,"text":"You see, in every country"},{"time":219120,"text":"where you hear about armed jihadis"},{"time":220970,"text":"targeting civilians,"},{"time":222726,"text":"there are also unarmed people"},{"time":224401,"text":"defying those militants that you don't hear about,"},{"time":227248,"text":"and those people need our support to succeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231830,"text":"In the West, it's often assumed"},{"time":233648,"text":"that Muslims generally condone terrorism."},{"time":236685,"text":"Some on the right think this because they view"},{"time":238687,"text":"Muslim culture as inherently violent,"},{"time":240950,"text":"and some on the left imagine this"},{"time":242535,"text":"because they view Muslim violence,"},{"time":244323,"text":"fundamentalist violence,"},{"time":245674,"text":"solely as a product of legitimate grievances."},{"time":249307,"text":"But both views are dead wrong."},{"time":251804,"text":"In fact, many people of Muslim heritage"},{"time":253619,"text":"around the world are staunch opponents"},{"time":256383,"text":"both of fundamentalism and of terrorism,"},{"time":259644,"text":"and often for very good reason."},{"time":262110,"text":"You see, they're much more likely to be victims"},{"time":264150,"text":"of this violence than its perpetrators."},{"time":267305,"text":"Let me just give you one example."},{"time":269322,"text":"According to a 2009 survey"},{"time":272165,"text":"of Arabic language media resources,"},{"time":274505,"text":"between 2004 and 2008,"},{"time":277756,"text":"no more than 15 percent of al Qaeda's victims"},{"time":280880,"text":"were Westerners."},{"time":282461,"text":"That's a terrible toll, but the vast majority"},{"time":285406,"text":"were people of Muslim heritage,"},{"time":287175,"text":"killed by Muslim fundamentalists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289991,"text":"Now I've been talking for the last five minutes"},{"time":292819,"text":"about fundamentalism, and you have a right to know"},{"time":295302,"text":"exactly what I mean."},{"time":296996,"text":"I cite the definition given by the Algerian sociologist"},{"time":300901,"text":"Marieme Helie Lucas,"},{"time":302940,"text":"and she says that fundamentalisms,"},{"time":305336,"text":"note the \"s,\" so within all of the world's"},{"time":307834,"text":"great religious traditions,"},{"time":309656,"text":"\"fundamentalisms are political\nmovements of the extreme right"},{"time":313627,"text":"which in a context of globalization"},{"time":315790,"text":"manipulate religion in order to achieve"},{"time":318284,"text":"their political aims.\""},{"time":319933,"text":"Sadia Abbas has called this the radical politicization"},{"time":323616,"text":"of theology."},{"time":325127,"text":"Now I want to avoid projecting the notion"},{"time":327542,"text":"that there's sort of a monolith out there"},{"time":329328,"text":"called Muslim fundamentalism\nthat is the same everywhere,"},{"time":332541,"text":"because these movements\nalso have their diversities."},{"time":335257,"text":"Some use and advocate violence."},{"time":337720,"text":"Some do not, though they're often interrelated."},{"time":340350,"text":"They take different forms."},{"time":341920,"text":"Some may be non-governmental organizations,"},{"time":344544,"text":"even here in Britain like Cageprisoners."},{"time":347076,"text":"Some may become political parties,"},{"time":349169,"text":"like the Muslim Brotherhood,"},{"time":350740,"text":"and some may be openly armed groups"},{"time":352458,"text":"like the Taliban."},{"time":354183,"text":"But in any case, these are all radical projects."},{"time":357504,"text":"They're not conservative or traditional approaches."},{"time":360733,"text":"They're most often about changing\npeople's relationship with Islam"},{"time":363946,"text":"rather than preserving it."},{"time":365501,"text":"What I am talking about is the Muslim extreme right,"},{"time":368891,"text":"and the fact that its adherents are"},{"time":370890,"text":"or purport to be Muslim"},{"time":372730,"text":"makes them no less offensive"},{"time":374140,"text":"than the extreme right anywhere else."},{"time":376631,"text":"So in my view, if we consider ourselves"},{"time":378498,"text":"liberal or left-wing,"},{"time":380248,"text":"human rights-loving or feminist,"},{"time":382708,"text":"we must oppose these movements"},{"time":384909,"text":"and support their grassroots opponents."},{"time":387754,"text":"Now let me be clear"},{"time":389370,"text":"that I support an effective struggle"},{"time":391372,"text":"against fundamentalism,"},{"time":393317,"text":"but also a struggle that must itself"},{"time":395597,"text":"respect international law,"},{"time":397535,"text":"so nothing I am saying should be taken"},{"time":399964,"text":"as a justification for refusals"},{"time":401809,"text":"to democratize,"},{"time":403274,"text":"and here I send out a shout-out of support"},{"time":405949,"text":"to the pro-democracy movement \nin Algeria today, Barakat."},{"time":410000,"text":"Nor should anything I say be taken"},{"time":412282,"text":"as a justification of violations of human rights,"},{"time":415149,"text":"like the mass death sentences"},{"time":416555,"text":"handed out in Egypt earlier this week."},{"time":419475,"text":"But what I am saying"},{"time":420998,"text":"is that we must challenge these\nMuslim fundamentalist movements"},{"time":424305,"text":"because they threaten human rights"},{"time":426123,"text":"across Muslim-majority contexts,"},{"time":428706,"text":"and they do this in a range of ways,"},{"time":431087,"text":"most obviously with the direct attacks on civilians"},{"time":434050,"text":"by the armed groups that carry those out."},{"time":436289,"text":"But that violence is just the tip of the iceberg."},{"time":439336,"text":"These movements as a whole purvey discrimination"},{"time":442127,"text":"against religious minorities and sexual minorities."},{"time":445448,"text":"They seek to curtail the freedom of religion"},{"time":447528,"text":"of everyone who either practices in a different way"},{"time":450427,"text":"or chooses not to practice."},{"time":452391,"text":"And most definingly, they lead an all-out war"},{"time":455815,"text":"on the rights of women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457896,"text":"Now, faced with these movements"},{"time":459692,"text":"in recent years, Western discourse"},{"time":461264,"text":"has most often offered"},{"time":462899,"text":"two flawed responses."},{"time":465156,"text":"The first that one sometimes finds on the right"},{"time":467719,"text":"suggests that most Muslims are fundamentalist"},{"time":470261,"text":"or something about Islam is\ninherently fundamentalist,"},{"time":473607,"text":"and this is just offensive and wrong,"},{"time":476898,"text":"but unfortunately on the left\none sometimes encounters"},{"time":479306,"text":"a discourse that is too politically correct"},{"time":481488,"text":"to acknowledge the problem of\nMuslim fundamentalism at all"},{"time":485290,"text":"or, even worse, apologizes for it,"},{"time":487651,"text":"and this is unacceptable as well."},{"time":490199,"text":"So what I'm seeking is a new way"},{"time":492261,"text":"of talking about this all together,"},{"time":494382,"text":"which is grounded in the lived experiences"},{"time":497110,"text":"and the hope of the people on the front lines."},{"time":500059,"text":"I'm painfully aware that there has been"},{"time":502010,"text":"an increase in discrimination\nagainst Muslims in recent years"},{"time":505191,"text":"in countries like the U.K. and the U.S.,"},{"time":507662,"text":"and that too is a matter of grave concern,"},{"time":510716,"text":"but I firmly believe"},{"time":511855,"text":"that telling these counter-stereotypical stories"},{"time":514816,"text":"of people of Muslim heritage"},{"time":516142,"text":"who have confronted the fundamentalists"},{"time":518314,"text":"and been their primary victims"},{"time":520329,"text":"is also a great way of countering that discrimination."},{"time":524906,"text":"So now let me introduce you"},{"time":526686,"text":"to four people whose stories"},{"time":528342,"text":"I had the great honor of telling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531558,"text":"Faizan Peerzada and the Rafi Peer Theatre"},{"time":533791,"text":"workshop named for his father"},{"time":535793,"text":"have for years promoted the performing arts"},{"time":537931,"text":"in Pakistan."},{"time":539663,"text":"With the rise of jihadist violence,"},{"time":541124,"text":"they began to receive threats"},{"time":542700,"text":"to call off their events, which they refused to heed."},{"time":545950,"text":"And so a bomber struck their 2008"},{"time":549220,"text":"eighth world performing arts festival in Lahore,"},{"time":552104,"text":"producing rain of glass"},{"time":553792,"text":"that fell into the venue"},{"time":555457,"text":"injuring nine people,"},{"time":557392,"text":"and later that same night,"},{"time":558960,"text":"the Peerzadas made a very difficult decision:"},{"time":561711,"text":"they announced that their festival"},{"time":563580,"text":"would continue as planned the next day."},{"time":566987,"text":"As Faizan said at the time,"},{"time":568438,"text":"if we bow down to the Islamists,"},{"time":570380,"text":"we'll just be sitting in a dark corner."},{"time":573491,"text":"But they didn't know what would happen."},{"time":575149,"text":"Would anyone come?"},{"time":577586,"text":"In fact, thousands of people came out the next day"},{"time":580475,"text":"to support the performing arts in Lahore,"},{"time":582877,"text":"and this simultaneously thrilled"},{"time":584722,"text":"and terrified Faizan,"},{"time":586544,"text":"and he ran up to a woman"},{"time":587997,"text":"who had come in with her two small children,"},{"time":590214,"text":"and he said, \"You do know there\nwas a bomb here yesterday,"},{"time":593408,"text":"and you do know there's a threat here today.\""},{"time":595735,"text":"And she said, \"I know that,"},{"time":597618,"text":"but I came to your festival"},{"time":599182,"text":"with my mother when I was their age,"},{"time":601612,"text":"and I still have those images in my mind."},{"time":604660,"text":"We have to be here.\""},{"time":606798,"text":"With stalwart audiences like this,"},{"time":608655,"text":"the Peerzadas were able to conclude"},{"time":610309,"text":"their festival on schedule."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612769,"text":"And then the next year,"},{"time":614006,"text":"they lost all of their sponsors"},{"time":615889,"text":"due to the security risk."},{"time":618258,"text":"So when I met them in 2010,"},{"time":620558,"text":"they were in the middle of the first subsequent event"},{"time":622844,"text":"that they were able to have in the same venue,"},{"time":625910,"text":"and this was the ninth youth performing arts festival"},{"time":629174,"text":"held in Lahore in a year when that city"},{"time":632149,"text":"had already experienced 44 terror attacks."},{"time":636219,"text":"This was a time when the Pakistani Taliban"},{"time":638322,"text":"had commenced their systematic targeting"},{"time":640139,"text":"of girls' schools that would culminate"},{"time":642347,"text":"in the attack on Malala Yousafzai."},{"time":645106,"text":"What did the Peerzadas do in that environment?"},{"time":649501,"text":"They staged girls' school theater."},{"time":652674,"text":"So I had the privilege of watching \"Naang Wal,\""},{"time":655486,"text":"which was a musical in the Punjabi language,"},{"time":658118,"text":"and the girls of Lahore Grammar School"},{"time":659880,"text":"played all the parts."},{"time":661606,"text":"They sang and danced,"},{"time":662840,"text":"they played the mice and the water buffalo,"},{"time":665498,"text":"and I held my breath, wondering,"},{"time":667962,"text":"would we get to the end"},{"time":669229,"text":"of this amazing show?"},{"time":671515,"text":"And when we did, the whole audience"},{"time":674071,"text":"collectively exhaled,"},{"time":675809,"text":"and a few people actually wept,"},{"time":678073,"text":"and then they filled the auditorium"},{"time":680596,"text":"with the peaceful boom of their applause."},{"time":683435,"text":"And I remember thinking in that moment"},{"time":686422,"text":"that the bombers made headlines here"},{"time":688853,"text":"two years before"},{"time":690516,"text":"but this night and these people"},{"time":692880,"text":"are as important a story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":698488,"text":"Maria Bashir is the first and only"},{"time":700968,"text":"woman chief prosecutor in Afghanistan."},{"time":704092,"text":"She's been in the post since 2008"},{"time":706306,"text":"and actually opened an office to investigate"},{"time":708492,"text":"cases of violence against women,"},{"time":710318,"text":"which she says is the most important area"},{"time":712576,"text":"in her mandate."},{"time":714310,"text":"When I meet her in her office in Herat,"},{"time":717375,"text":"she enters surrounded by"},{"time":719120,"text":"four large men with four huge guns."},{"time":722486,"text":"In fact, she now has 23 bodyguards,"},{"time":725450,"text":"because she has weathered bomb attacks"},{"time":726870,"text":"that nearly killed her kids,"},{"time":728548,"text":"and it took the leg off of one of her guards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731899,"text":"Why does she continue?"},{"time":734009,"text":"She says with a smile that that is the question"},{"time":736663,"text":"that everyone asks—"},{"time":738710,"text":"as she puts it, \"Why you risk not living?\""},{"time":742535,"text":"And it is simply that for her,"},{"time":744174,"text":"a better future for all the Maria Bashirs to come"},{"time":747643,"text":"is worth the risk,"},{"time":749127,"text":"and she knows that if people like her"},{"time":750837,"text":"do not take the risk,"},{"time":752752,"text":"there will be no better future."},{"time":755049,"text":"Later on in our interview,"},{"time":756776,"text":"Prosecutor Bashir tells me how worried she is"},{"time":759139,"text":"about the possible outcome"},{"time":760658,"text":"of government negotiations with the Taliban,"},{"time":763157,"text":"the people who have been trying to kill her."},{"time":765551,"text":"\"If we give them a place in the government,\""},{"time":767303,"text":"she asks, \"Who will protect women's rights?\""},{"time":770520,"text":"And she urges the international community"},{"time":772886,"text":"not to forget its promise about women"},{"time":775518,"text":"because now they want peace with Taliban."},{"time":779345,"text":"A few weeks after I leave Afghanistan,"},{"time":781550,"text":"I see a headline on the Internet."},{"time":784425,"text":"An Afghan prosecutor has been assassinated."},{"time":788030,"text":"I google desperately,"},{"time":790166,"text":"and thankfully that day I find out"},{"time":791840,"text":"that Maria was not the victim,"},{"time":793926,"text":"though sadly, another Afghan prosecutor"},{"time":796149,"text":"was gunned down on his way to work."},{"time":798180,"text":"And when I hear headlines like that now,"},{"time":801175,"text":"I think that as international troops"},{"time":803473,"text":"leave Afghanistan this year and beyond,"},{"time":806521,"text":"we must continue to care"},{"time":808427,"text":"about what happens to people there,"},{"time":809860,"text":"to all of the Maria Bashirs."},{"time":812886,"text":"Sometimes I still hear her voice in my head"},{"time":815499,"text":"saying, with no bravado whatsoever,"},{"time":818580,"text":"\"The situation of the women of Afghanistan"},{"time":821185,"text":"will be better someday."},{"time":823091,"text":"We should prepare the ground for this,"},{"time":825326,"text":"even if we are killed.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":829854,"text":"There are no words adequate"},{"time":831502,"text":"to denounce the al Shabaab terrorists"},{"time":833478,"text":"who attacked the Westgate Mall in Nairobi"},{"time":835740,"text":"on the same day as a children's cooking competition"},{"time":839202,"text":"in September of 2013."},{"time":841620,"text":"They killed 67, including poets and pregnant women."},{"time":846119,"text":"Far away in the American Midwest,"},{"time":848218,"text":"I had the good fortune of meeting Somali-Americans"},{"time":850565,"text":"who were working to counter\nthe efforts of al Shabaab"},{"time":853413,"text":"to recruit a small number of young people"},{"time":855637,"text":"from their city of Minneapolis"},{"time":857581,"text":"to take part in atrocities like Westgate."},{"time":861279,"text":"Abdirizak Bihi's studious"},{"time":863239,"text":"17-year-old nephew Burhan Hassan"},{"time":866128,"text":"was recruited here in 2008,"},{"time":868776,"text":"spirited to Somalia,"},{"time":870536,"text":"and then killed when he tried to come home."},{"time":873906,"text":"Since that time, Mr. Bihi,"},{"time":875500,"text":"who directs the no-budget Somali\nEducation and Advocacy Center,"},{"time":879753,"text":"has been vocally denouncing the recruitment"},{"time":882204,"text":"and the failures of government"},{"time":884060,"text":"and Somali-American institutions"},{"time":886279,"text":"like the Abubakar As-Saddique Islamic Center"},{"time":889304,"text":"where he believes his nephew was radicalized"},{"time":891535,"text":"during a youth program."},{"time":893641,"text":"But he doesn't just criticize the mosque."},{"time":895794,"text":"He also takes on the government"},{"time":897373,"text":"for its failure to do more"},{"time":899158,"text":"to prevent poverty in his community."},{"time":901656,"text":"Given his own lack of financial resources,"},{"time":903945,"text":"Mr. Bihi has had to be creative."},{"time":906256,"text":"To counter the efforts of al Shabaab"},{"time":908150,"text":"to sway more disaffected youth,"},{"time":910535,"text":"in the wake of the group's 2010 attack"},{"time":912970,"text":"on World Cup viewers in Uganda,"},{"time":915564,"text":"he organized a Ramadan basketball tournament"},{"time":918904,"text":"in Minneapolis in response."},{"time":921436,"text":"Scores of Somali-American kids came out"},{"time":924120,"text":"to embrace sport"},{"time":925508,"text":"despite the fatwa against it."},{"time":928000,"text":"They played basketball"},{"time":929745,"text":"as Burhan Hassan never would again."},{"time":933612,"text":"For his efforts, Mr. Bihi has been ostracized"},{"time":936262,"text":"by the leadership of the Abubakar\nAs-Saddique Islamic Center,"},{"time":939334,"text":"with which he used to have good relations."},{"time":941899,"text":"He told me, \"One day we saw the imam on TV"},{"time":944285,"text":"calling us infidels and saying,"},{"time":946343,"text":"'These families are trying to destroy the mosque.'\""},{"time":949912,"text":"This is at complete odds"},{"time":951323,"text":"with how Abdirizak Bihi understands"},{"time":953856,"text":"what he is trying to do"},{"time":955656,"text":"by exposing al Shabaab recruitment,"},{"time":958062,"text":"which is to save the religion I love"},{"time":960484,"text":"from a small number of extremists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":964938,"text":"Now I want to tell one last story,"},{"time":967499,"text":"that of a 22-year-old law student in Algeria"},{"time":970513,"text":"named Amel Zenoune-Zouani"},{"time":972459,"text":"who had the same dreams of a legal career"},{"time":974338,"text":"that I did back in the '90s."},{"time":977040,"text":"She refused to give up her studies,"},{"time":978969,"text":"despite the fact that the fundamentalists"},{"time":980938,"text":"battling the Algerian state back then"},{"time":983468,"text":"threatened all who continued their education."},{"time":987090,"text":"On January 26, 1997, Amel boarded the bus"},{"time":991200,"text":"in Algiers where she was studying"},{"time":993122,"text":"to go home and spend a Ramadan evening"},{"time":995305,"text":"with her family,"},{"time":996994,"text":"and would never finish law school."},{"time":999380,"text":"When the bus reached the outskirts"},{"time":1000840,"text":"of her hometown, it was stopped"},{"time":1002615,"text":"at a checkpoint manned by men"},{"time":1004757,"text":"from the Armed Islamic Group."},{"time":1007051,"text":"Carrying her schoolbag,"},{"time":1008780,"text":"Amel was taken off the bus"},{"time":1010766,"text":"and killed in the street."},{"time":1013355,"text":"The men who cut her throat"},{"time":1014491,"text":"then told everyone else,"},{"time":1016341,"text":"\"If you go to university,"},{"time":1018235,"text":"the day will come when we will kill all of you"},{"time":1020789,"text":"just like this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1024020,"text":"Amel died at exactly 5:17 p.m.,"},{"time":1026720,"text":"which we know because when she fell in the street,"},{"time":1029568,"text":"her watch broke."},{"time":1031345,"text":"Her mother showed me the watch"},{"time":1032574,"text":"with the second hand still aimed"},{"time":1034575,"text":"optimistically upward"},{"time":1036071,"text":"towards a 5:18 that would never come."},{"time":1039507,"text":"Shortly before her death,"},{"time":1040656,"text":"Amel had said to her mother of herself"},{"time":1042511,"text":"and her sisters,"},{"time":1044398,"text":"\"Nothing will happen to us, Inshallah, God willing,"},{"time":1048015,"text":"but if something happens,"},{"time":1049885,"text":"you must know that we are dead for knowledge."},{"time":1052768,"text":"You and father must keep your heads held high.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1056978,"text":"The loss of such a young woman is unfathomable,"},{"time":1060960,"text":"and so as I did my research"},{"time":1062515,"text":"I found myself searching for Amel's hope again"},{"time":1065769,"text":"and her name even means \"hope\" in Arabic."},{"time":1068706,"text":"I think I found it in two places."},{"time":1071957,"text":"The first is in the strength of her family"},{"time":1074252,"text":"and all the other families to\ncontinue telling their stories"},{"time":1077518,"text":"and to go on with their lives despite the terrorism."},{"time":1080583,"text":"In fact, Amel's sister Lamia overcame her grief,"},{"time":1083865,"text":"went to law school,"},{"time":1085236,"text":"and practices as a lawyer in Algiers today,"},{"time":1087990,"text":"something which is only possible"},{"time":1089591,"text":"because the armed fundamentalists"},{"time":1090780,"text":"were largely defeated in the country."},{"time":1093658,"text":"And the second place I found Amel's hope"},{"time":1096505,"text":"was everywhere that women and men"},{"time":1098977,"text":"continue to defy the jihadis."},{"time":1101672,"text":"We must support all of those in honor of Amel"},{"time":1104930,"text":"who continue this human rights struggle today,"},{"time":1107563,"text":"like the Network of Women\nLiving Under Muslim Laws."},{"time":1111560,"text":"It is not enough, as the victims rights advocate"},{"time":1114187,"text":"Cherifa Kheddar told me in Algiers,"},{"time":1116074,"text":"it is not enough just to battle terrorism."},{"time":1119139,"text":"We must also challenge fundamentalism,"},{"time":1121683,"text":"because fundamentalism is the ideology"},{"time":1124120,"text":"that makes the bed of this terrorism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1126711,"text":"Why is it that people like her, like all of them"},{"time":1130150,"text":"are not more well known?"},{"time":1131844,"text":"Why is it that everyone knows\nwho Osama bin Laden was"},{"time":1135121,"text":"and so few know of all of those"},{"time":1137054,"text":"standing up to the bin Ladens in their own contexts."},{"time":1140747,"text":"We must change that, and so I ask you"},{"time":1143404,"text":"to please help share these stories"},{"time":1145172,"text":"through your networks."},{"time":1146945,"text":"Look again at Amel Zenoune's watch,"},{"time":1149044,"text":"forever frozen,"},{"time":1150704,"text":"and now please look at your own watch"},{"time":1153066,"text":"and decide this is the moment that you commit"},{"time":1156090,"text":"to supporting people like Amel."},{"time":1157998,"text":"We don't have the right to be silent about them"},{"time":1160379,"text":"because it is easier"},{"time":1161877,"text":"or because Western policy is flawed as well,"},{"time":1164738,"text":"because 5:17 is still coming"},{"time":1167074,"text":"to too many Amel Zenounes"},{"time":1168941,"text":"in places like northern Nigeria,"},{"time":1170911,"text":"where jihadis still kill students."},{"time":1173487,"text":"The time to speak up in support of all of those"},{"time":1176568,"text":"who peacefully challenge fundamentalism"},{"time":1178876,"text":"and terrorism in their own communities"},{"time":1181840,"text":"is now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1183376,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1185659,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}